IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
    PROGRAM-ID. ControlFlowExample.
    AUTHOR. CENTRA-NF Team.
    VERSION. 0-2-0.

ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
    OS "Linux".
    ARCH "x86_64".
    RUNTIME-VERSION "1.0".

DATA DIVISION.
    INPUT VIDEO-MP4 AS VIDEO-STREAM.
    INPUT BINARY-BLOB AS BLOB-DATA.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    IF CONDITION THEN
        COMPRESS VIDEO-STREAM.
        VERIFY-INTEGRITY VIDEO-STREAM.
    END-IF.
    FOR ITEM IN LIST DO
        COMPRESS BLOB-DATA.
    END-FOR.
    WHILE FLAG DO
        VERIFY-INTEGRITY BLOB-DATA.
    END-WHILE.